; ============================================================
; Phase 2 Validation: Characters and Backgrounds
; ============================================================
; Tests all GITT characters (with appearances) and backgrounds.
; Run to verify all actors are registered and display correctly.
; ============================================================

@printer TADialogue

; --- Background: Office ---
@back Office
This is the Office background. Hanna's law firm office — where Act 1 takes place.

; --- Character: Hanna (all appearances) ---
@char Hanna pos:50
Hanna: This is Hanna — default appearance.
@char Hanna.Wheelchair
Hanna: Now showing Wheelchair appearance.
@char Hanna.Suspicious
Hanna: Suspicious appearance.
@char Hanna.Angry
Hanna: Angry appearance.
@char Hanna.Smirking
Hanna: Smirking appearance.
@char Hanna.Tearful
Hanna: Tearful appearance.
@char Hanna.Pain
Hanna: Pain appearance.
@char Hanna.Tender
Hanna: Tender appearance.
@hide Hanna

; --- Character: Mat (all appearances) ---
@char Mat pos:50
Mat: This is Mat — default appearance.
@char Mat.Suit
Mat: Suit appearance.
@char Mat.Kneeling
Mat: Kneeling appearance.
@char Mat.Sympathetic
Mat: Sympathetic appearance.
@char Mat.Emotional
Mat: Emotional appearance.
@char Mat.Scrubs
Mat: Scrubs appearance.
@char Mat.Shocked
Mat: Shocked appearance.
@char Mat.Enraged
Mat: Enraged appearance.
@hide Mat

; --- Character: Nurse (all appearances) ---
@char Nurse pos:50
Nurse: This is Nurse — default appearance.
@char Nurse.Professional
Nurse: Professional appearance.
@char Nurse.Protective
Nurse: Protective appearance.
@hide Nurse

; --- Character: Doctor (all appearances) ---
@char Doctor pos:50
Doctor: This is Doctor — default appearance.
@char Doctor.Calm
Doctor: Calm appearance.
@char Doctor.Urgent
Doctor: Urgent appearance.
@hide Doctor

; --- Multiple characters on stage ---
@back Office
@char Hanna.Wheelchair pos:25
@char Mat.Suit pos:75
Hanna: Mat and I are both on screen now.
Mat: Two characters positioned side by side.

; --- Three characters ---
@char Nurse.Professional pos:50
Nurse: Now there are three of us.
@hide Nurse
@hide Hanna
@hide Mat

; --- Background: OperatingRoom ---
@back OperatingRoom
This is the Operating Room background. Standard hospital OR.

@char Doctor.Calm pos:30
@char Nurse.Professional pos:70
Doctor: The operating room before the reveal.
Nurse: Everything looks normal so far.
@hide Doctor
@hide Nurse

; --- Background: OperatingRoomRevealed ---
@back OperatingRoomRevealed
This is the Operating Room Revealed — after the centaur transformation is visible.

@char Mat.Scrubs pos:50
Mat: The room has changed. The truth is visible now.
@hide Mat

; --- Background: Black (transition) ---
@back Black
This is the Black background — used for transitions and blackouts.

; --- Background transitions ---
@back Office time:1 wait!
Smooth transition to Office over 1 second.
@back OperatingRoom time:1 wait!
Smooth transition to Operating Room.
@back Black time:0.5 wait!

; --- Final combined test ---
@back Office time:0.5 wait!
@char Hanna.Angry pos:30
@char Mat.Sympathetic pos:70
Hanna: This is a full scene setup — background, two characters, specific appearances.
Mat: If you can see us both with the Office behind us, Phase 2 is working.
@hide Hanna
@hide Mat

; --- End ---
@back Black time:0.5 wait!
Phase 2 validation complete. All characters, appearances, and backgrounds are registered.
@stop
